%N A368604 Irregular triangular array T, read by rows: T(n,k) = number of sums |x-y|+|y-z| = k, where x,y,z are in {1,2,...,n} and x < y and y > z.
%C A368604 The difference sequence of the k-th column is (k), for k >= 1.
%e A368604 First nine rows:
%e A368604   0
